Ibyago byo kwandura icyorezo cya coronavirus (COVID-19) byiyongereye mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Ubukungu bw'Ibihugu by'i Burayi no mu Bwongereza, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) kigaragaza ibintu nk'ibi mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza byemeza ko, mu gihe ku rwego rutandukanye bitewe n'igihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Dukurikije ibihamya biturutse mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bazima bikwiye kongera imyiteguro ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bazongera kwiyongera bazakenera ubuvuzi, cyane cyane ubuvuzi bwagutse.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, hari icyorezo cya pneumonia kitamenyekanye mu bwoko bwacyo cyatangajwe i Wuhan, mu Ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko ari icyorezo gishya cya coronavirus cyiswe SARS-COV-2 (Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome).
Kuva icyo gihe, icyorezo cyatewe n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 cyiswe coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, ibihamya bigaragaza ko hafi 80% by'abantu banduye COVID-19 barwaye indwara yoroheje, ni ukuvuga indwara z'ubuhumekero ziterwa n'ibicurane by'ibihaha cyangwa nta ndwara y'ibicurane, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu barwayi 14%, COVID-19 ikomeza kuba ndwara ikomeye cyane isaba ko umuntu arara mu bitaro mu gihe 6% by'abarwayi bagerwaho n'indwara ikomeye cyane isaba kwitabwaho cyane.
Umubare w'abarwayi bapfa mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye impinduka mu byorezo bya COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cy'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ibihugu by'Iburayi (EU/EEA) n'u Bwongereza (Ubwongereza) tugereranya n'ibyo mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Turagereranya kandi imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza n'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 ikomeje gukwirakwira mu bihugu bitandukanye kandi umuvuduko w'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bihugu byo ku isi ubu urakurikirana iki gihugu.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu nomero yo ku ya 5 Werurwe ya Eurosurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al. ni bo ba mbere mu Burayi bemeje ko hari umuntu wanduye COVID-19 hakurikijwe uko OMS ibibona.
Mu karere ka EU/EEA, u Bufaransa bwagaragaje ubwandu bwa mbere butatu ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bagarutse bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, hari hamaze kuboneka ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu byose 30 bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, aho hagati ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 n'uwo munsi, hari hamaze kuboneka abarwayi 39,768 n'abantu 1,727 bapfuye, hamwe n'abantu 17,750 banduye n'abantu 1,441 bapfuye mu Butaliyani honyine.
Kubona umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 hamwe n'ibimenyetso byabyo
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara (ECDC), gitanga imibare ya COVID-19 mu bihugu byose byo ku isi, iboneka gusa mu makuru yemewe nk'ibiro by'ubuzima by'ibihugu, inzego z'ubuzima mpuzamahanga na OMS na OMS, iherutse kuvugururwa buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma imiterere ya COVID-19 muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, agereranywa n'iyo mu Butaliyani.
Nk'umuhagarariye w'ibyabaye mu gihe cya COVID-19, twabaze iminsi 14 y'ibyabaye mu gihe cya COVID-19, bityo tureba uko COVID-19 yagenze, muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, hagati ya tariki ya 1 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twanashyizeho kandi imibare y'ibanze y'ubwandu muri buri gihugu ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani za mu gitondo ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibereho ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza
Impinduka mu minsi 14 y'igiteranyo cy'ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza muri rusange byibanze mu ntara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Ikubo rya 1).
Ku bihugu byo muri EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza muri rusange, umubare w'abandura COVID-19 watangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare hanyuma wiyongera cyane ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (ibikoresho by'inyongera).
Ibi byatewe n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'umubare w'abanduye baturutse mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza na byo byerekana ko hari umubare munini w'abanduye COVID-19 (Ibitero by'umurengera).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza ubwandu bwa COVID-19, mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK ugereranyije n'Ubutaliyani ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
Igaragaza ko ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani za mu gitondo, ibihugu 15 bya EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza byari bimaze gutangaza abanduye ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani mu byumweru 3 bishize cyangwa munsi yaho.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu byerekana ko umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 wiyongera mu buryo bwihuse muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibyagaragariye mu by'ibanze ku byabaye kuri COVID-19 byerekana ko icyorezo cyateye imbere mu buryo bwihuse kandi bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Ibi ni mu gihe ibihugu biri mu byiciro bitandukanye, mu bisubizo by'ubuzima rusange by'igihugu, kandi bishoboka ko mu bihugu bitandukanye hari amategeko atandukanye agenga guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo bamenye COVID-19, harimo no gupimwa.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere twibasiwe na COVID-19 mu Butaliyani bagaragaje ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane kandi itangazamakuru ryatangaje ko ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi cyane muri utwo turere byari bimaze kugera ku bushobozi bwabyo.
Amakuru ajyanye n'abarwayi bavurirwa mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 na/cyangwa mu bigo byita ku barwayi barembye ubu aboneka ku rwego rwa EU/EEA ku bantu 6% gusa na 1% by'abarwaye, ku buryo butandukanye (amakuru ntabwo agaragaza).
Ariko kandi, bigomba gukusanywa mu buryo buhuje n'amakuru y'ubugenzuzi y'ubu, yibanda ku raporo z'ubwandu n'imfu.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2010-11 bwagaragaje itandukaniro rinini mu kuboneka kw'ibitanda by'indembe n'iby'abarezi mu Burayi, kuva ku bitanda 29.2 mu Budage kugeza ku bitanda 4.2 ku baturage 100.000 muri Porutugali.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kuba bifite umutungo uri hasi cyangwa uri hasi cyane ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (12.5 ibitanda byo mu bitaro byagutse n'iby'abarezi ba bwite ku baturage 100,000 mu 2010-11).
Imiterere yo kugenzura ishingiye ku bufatanye bw'ibigo by'ubuvuzi, imibare ya buri gihugu cya EU/EEA na UK n'ubudehe bw'ibitaro ku barwayi ba COVID-19 buhuye na &gt; > 90% n'ibyago byinshi byo kurara ku buriri, byatanzwe mu isubiramo rya gatandatu rya ECDC ry'igeragezwa ryihuse ry'ibyago bya COVID-19.
Kubera ko ubwandu bw'indwara buri mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe bya EU/EEA na UK, ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bw'indwara zikomeye akenshi bifasha abaturage bo mu karere bazwi, amakuru ajyanye n'ubwandu n'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi byashoboraga kuboneka neza ku rwego rwa Nomenclature y'ibice by'akarere ku rwego rwa 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwiga mu Butaliyani n'ibyabaye mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bazima bigomba kwitegura uburyo bwo gukwirakwiza SARS-CoV-2 mu baturage no kwiyongera kw'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, hamwe n'ubwisungane mu kwivuza, nk'uko bigenda mu turere tw'u Butaliyani twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Nkuko byagaragajwe mu bushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa na ECDC ku iterambere ry'ibyago, ibikorwa byihuse, byuzuye kandi byuzuye ni ngombwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, hamwe no kuva ku buryo bwo kwinjiza ukagera ku buryo bwo kugabanya, kuko kwiyongera vuba kw'umubare w'ubwandu bidashobora guha abajyanama n'ibitaro igihe cy'umwanya wose kugirango basobanukirwe, bemere kandi bahindure uburyo bwo gukora mbere y'igihe.
Ubushakashatsi bw'ibyago bwihuse kandi bugaragaza ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hari uburyo bugufi bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo mu gihe ibihugu bifite amahirwe yo kongera imbaraga mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya ibibazo by'ubuzima.
Ibi byavuzwe, birashoboka ko gahunda y'ubuzima mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe bya EU/EEA ishobora guhura n'umubare munini w'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane mu minsi cyangwa ibyumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'indwara ifata imyanya y'ubuhumekero ikomeye (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,000 kandi cyandura abantu barenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, cyabaye ibyago ku bantu.
Kimwe na virusi imwe, SARS-CoV, yateje SARS mu bihumbi by'abantu mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 nayo ishobora kwanduzwa n'imbeba kandi igatera ibimenyetso nk'ibyo mu buryo bumwe.
Icyakora, COVID-19 ifite ubukana buke kandi yica kurusha SARS ariko ikwirakwira cyane kandi ikagira ingaruka ku bantu bakuze kurusha abakiri bato n'abagabo kurusha abagore.
Mu rwego rwo gusubiza umubare munini w'ibitabo byatangajwe vuba ku ndwara iri kuvuka, iyi nkuru igerageza gutanga ubushakashatsi bwimbitse ku iterambere ry'ikibazo cy'ubushakashatsi bwihuse.
Tuzamenya ibintu by'ibanze ku byerekeye indwara z'ibyorezo, indwara ziterwa n'indwara, virusi, ubushakashatsi, ubuvuzi, uko indwara zitezwa imbere n'uko zirinzwe.
Nubwo hakiri ibibazo byinshi bikeneye ibisubizo, twizeye ko iyi raporo izadufasha gusobanukirwa no kurwanya iki cyorezo giteye ubwoba.
Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi wo ku ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye umunsi utazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose basabwe kuguma mu rugo muri iyi minsi mikuru yose ndetse no mu byumweru byinshi nyuma y'icyorezo.
Iyi virusi isa cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yateje icyorezo gikomeye cy'indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero (SARS) mu 2003; bityo, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryayise SARS-CoV-2 ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, kandi indwara ifitanye isano na yo yitwa CoV Inzoka ya Covid-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, maze gikwirakwira mu gihugu hose kandi kigera ku bantu 50 ku isi hose.
Kuva ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi yatumye haboneka abarwayi barenga 80,000 banduye COVID-19, abarwayi barenga 40,000 bakize n'abarenga 3,000 bapfuye.
"WHO yaburiye ko COVID-19 ari ""umwanzi wa mbere ku isi"" kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba".
Nk'uko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, inyandiko zirenga 200 ku COVID-19 zanditswe harimo virology, epidemiology, etiology, diagnostics, na treatment kuva raporo ya mbere yo ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 yashyiraga ku rutonde indwara yari yaratoranyijwe mu barwayi benshi.
Iyi nyandiko igerageza gusobanura neza uko ubushakashatsi bwagenze mu ngingo nshya kandi ihinduka vuba.
Igihe cyose bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi CoV yateje icyorezo, indwara y'ubuhumekero ya Arabian hemorrhagic syndrome (MERS, mu 2012).
Nanone turi busuzume ibyo tumaze kumenya ku birebana no kwirinda indwara n'ibindi bibazo bikiriho.
CoVs zisanzwe zibonwa nk'indwara zidakomeye ku bantu, akenshi zitera hafi 15% by'ibicurane 4.
Nyamara, muri iki kinyejana, twahuye n'indwara ebyiri zandura ziterwa n'abantu, ari zo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatumye haba icyorezo mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi bidatinze cyakwirakwiriye mu bindi bihugu bihitana abantu benshi.
Ku bw'ibyo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni cyo cyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara mu ishusho. 1,1, abantu ba mbere banduye icyorezo cya pneumonia cyaturutse i Wuhan ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 babwiwe n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cy'Ubuzima cy'u Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, urutonde rw'inzira za CoV rwongeye gukurikiranwa.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, ni bwo bwa mbere habonetse umuntu wanduye indwara ya Wuhan.
Hagati aho, iyo ndwara yahise ikwira mu migi, intara n'ibihugu byo hafi aho.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, raporo yatanzwe n'abayobozi b'ubuzima, ivuga ko ubwandu bw'umuntu ku wundi bushoboka.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan wafunzwe kandi ingendo rusange zirahagarikwa.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bw'ibanze bw'abaganga kuri iki cyorezo bwagaragaje ko mu bantu 41 banduye, 21 gusa ari bo bahuye mu buryo butaziguye n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Wuhan ryakoreshejwe nk'aho icyorezo cyatangiriye.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi ku isi.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yatangazwaga, iki cyorezo cyari kimaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi hose (Igishushanyo cya 2).2)
Uko ibintu bizagenda byihuta, ni na ko bizagenda bigenda, kandi uko icyo cyorezo kizarushaho gukwirakwira bizagaragara.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo ku barwayi 8,866 barimo 4,021 banduye COVID-19 bwashyizwe ahagaragara amakuru mashya y'indwara nk'iyi ikurikira (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS ifata abantu b'imyaka yose, ariko ikunda gufata abantu bafite imyaka iri hagati ya 30 na 65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47.7%) cy'abanduye bari mu kigero cy'imyaka 50, bake cyane bari munsi y'imyaka 20, kandi abanduye bari munsi y'imyaka 10 ni 14 gusa.
SARS-CoV-2 yibasira cyane abagabo (0.31 / 100,000) kurusha abagore (0.27 / 100,000).
COVID-19 yageze mu karere ka Hubei no mu nkengero zayo.
COVID-19 imara iminsi 5 (2-9) kuva itangiye kugeza igihe isuzumwe.
Igihe ubwandu bukomeza gukwirakwira ni iminsi 4.8 (3.0-7.2).
Igihe cyo kuva ku ntangiriro kugeza ku gupfa ni iminsi 9.5 (4.8-13)
Umubare w'ibanze w'abana bavutse (R0) wari 3.77 (95% CI: 3.51-4.05), kandi ihame rya R0 ni 2.23-4.82.
Umubare w'abanduye wiyongereye cyane mbere ya 23 Mutarama 2020, bihuye n'igihe cyo kwishyura mbere y'umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi mu Bushinwa.
Umubare w'abarwayi bapfa bishwe n'ubwandu bw'ibicurane ni 1.44% (95% CI: 1.10-1.86%), kandi igipimo cy'abapfa bose ni 3.06% (95% CI: 2.02-4.59%).
Ibintu bitatu by'ingenzi bitera ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 ni igitsina (abagabo), imyaka (≥60), n'uburwayi bukabije bwa pneumonie.
CoV ni umuryango ugizwe n'inkingo nini z'indwara ziterwa na RNA imwe.
