Ibyinshi mu bikoresho by'ingenzi bikoreshwa muri iryo koranabuhanga ntibimenyekana cyangwa ntibisobanuke neza kubera ko bigoye gutandukanya no kwemeza ibyo bikoresho cyangwa ibyo bikoresho.
Muri iki gihe, kubera ubudahangarwa buke no kugenzura neza uburyo bwo kuvura COVID-19, TCM yabaye imwe mu nzira zikoreshwa cyane mu kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje kugeza ku burebure cyangwa abavuye mu ngamba zikomeye.
Urugero, imiti ya Shu Feng Jie Du na Lian Hua Qing Wen, yagaragaye ko ikwiriye mu kuvura COVID-19.
Iperereza ryakozwe ku barwayi ba COVID-19 mu ntara nyinshi z'Ubushinwa zikoresha TCM ku kigero cya 87% by'abarwayi babo, harimo Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%) na Hunan (50%), mu gihe intara ya Hubei, yakoresheje TCM ku kigero cya 30% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19, ifite igipimo cyo kugabanuka cyane (13%).
Icyakora, ibyo byaba ari ugupima nabi, kuko hari ibindi bintu bigira ingaruka, urugero nk'umubare w'abarwayi n'uburemere bwabo, bigomba gushyirwa mu ngengabitekerezo.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Boli Zhang na bagenzi be basohoye inyigo igereranya ubuvuzi bw'iburengerazuba (WM) buvura ubwabwo hamwe n'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze bwa WM na TCM.
Basanze igihe cyo gukira mu mubiri, guhumeka no kujya mu bitaro ari gito cyane mu itsinda rya WM + TCM ugereranyije n'itsinda rya WM gusa.
Igishishikaje kurushaho, ibikomere byongera uburwayi (kuva ku muvuduko woroshye kugeza ku buremere) byari bike mu itsinda rya WM + TCM kurusha iryo mu itsinda rya WM gusa ibice (7.4% hafi 46.2%) kandi umubare w'abapfa wari muto mu itsinda rya WM + TCM kuruta iryo mu itsinda rya WM gusa ibice (8.8% kuri 39%).
Ariko kandi, ubuziranenge n'ubuzima bwiza bwa TCM biracyategereje kugeragezwa mu buryo bufite ubushobozi ku kigero kinini no mu bigo byinshi.
Nanone kandi, byaba byiza umenye imiterere y'ibikorwa kandi ugasobanura ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bya TCM cyangwa se ibyo bihuriyeho, niba bishoboka.
