Icy'ingenzi hano ni ukumenya itandukaniro riri hagati ya virusi HCoVs no gusobanukirwa uko virusi ihinduka n'uko ingirabuzimafatizo zihinduka kuva ku nkomoko.
Icyorezo cya CoV 2019 (COVID-19) cyasobanuwe hano.
Byongeye kandi, hashimangiwe uburyo bukenewe kugira ngo virusi igire aho iba igenda ihinduka kandi hashimangiwe ingaruka z'ihindagurika ry'imiterere y'indwara.
Virusi za Corona (CoVs) ni zo zigize umuryango wa Coronaviridae, ugizwe n'itsinda ry'indwara z'umugongo umwe za RNA.
Izi virusi z'ubwandu zigizwe n'ubwoko bwinshi bwa RNA zisa na 26 kugeza kuri 32, ari nayo mpamvu zitwa CoVs zishobora kubonwa na mikorosikopi.
Mu by'ukuri, CoVs zifite imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo idasobanutse neza.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu by'iyo ADN biba birimo uturemangingo tubiri tw'ingenzi cyane (ORF1a na ORF1b), tugahindurwa pp1a na pp1ab duprotein.
Iyo poroteyine zongera gukorwamo izindi, zitanga za poroteyine 16 zitagira uko zimeze, zitondetse mu bwoko bwa nsp1~16.
Ibindi bice by'ingirabuzimafatizo birimo ORFs mu byiciro by'indwara, urugero nk'udupira (S), uruhago (E), uruhu (M) na nucleoprotein (N).
Ubwoko bwinshi bwa CoVs, na bwo bushobora kuba bufite ubwoko butandukanye bwa CoVs.
Bitewe n'itandukaniro mu miterere ya za poroteyine, CoVs zigizwe n'ibice bine (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV na delta-CoV), aho beta-CoV igizwe na HCoVs nyinshi kandi zigizwe n'ibice bine (A, B, C na D).
Ibihamya by'ibinyabuzima byerekana ko udusimba n'inyamaswa ari byo bikomoka kuri alpha-CoVs na beta-CoVs nyinshi, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zikomoka kuri gamma-CoVs na delta-CoVs nyinshi.
Mu myaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, CoVs zatsinze inzitizi z'ubwoko kandi zimwe muri zo zigize virusi z'ingenzi mu bantu.
Kugeza ubu, hari ubwoko burindwi bw'ubwandu bwa CoVs (HCoVs) buzwi mu bantu.
Muri izo, HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63 ni alpha-CoVs.
Izindi beta-CoV eshanu ni HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, icyorezo cy'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye (SARS-CoV), icyorezo cy'indwara z'ubuhumekero z'ibice by'Abarabu (MERS-CoV) na SARS-CoV-2.
Indwara za HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63 akenshi zitera ibimenyetso byoroheje nk'ibicurane cyangwa ibicurane.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV n'izindi ndwara zanduye za SARS-CoV-2 ni zo ndwara zisanzwe zitera uburwayi bukomeye mu barwayi bafite ibyago byinshi byo gutera indwara y'ubuhumekero budafite imbaraga (ARDS) n'ibimenyetso by'indwara.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E, B814, bwabonetse mu bwonko bw'abarwayi barwaye ibicurane mu myaka ya za 60 rwagati.
Kuva icyo gihe, ubumenyi ku ndwara ya HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 bwakomeje kwiyongera, binyuze mu kwiga ibimenyetso by'indwara.
Mu by'ukuri, kugeza igihe SARS yadutse, abantu benshi bemeraga ko kwandura HCoVs nta kibazo byateje.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu mwaka wa 2003, ni kimwe mu byorezo by'indwara mbi cyane mu mateka ya none, cyanduye abantu barenga 8,000 mu buryo bukabije, kigira igipimo cy'urupfu kiri hafi 10%.
Nyuma y'imyaka icumi, icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (Middle East Respiratory Syndrome, MERS) cyatumye haba icyorezo cy'indwara mu bihugu by'Abarabu, kandi cyakwirakwiriye mu bindi bice by'isi.
Icyorezo cya HCoV cyo mu 2019 (2019-nCoV), cyaje kwitwa SARS-CoV-2, ni cyo cyatumye habaho icyorezo cya coronavirus cy'ubwoko bushya cya 2019 (COVID-19), cyahitanye abantu barenga 3,120 kandi cyandura abantu barenga 91,000 mu kwezi kwa gatatu mu 2020.
Ibikangisho birumvikana kandi isi igomba kwitegura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kiri hafi.
HCoVs zose uko ari ndwi zaturutse ku nyamaswa zirimo udusimba, imbeba cyangwa amatungo.
Ibihamya byinshi bishyigikira ko HCoVs zose zakomotse ku nguge, aho virusi zisanzwe zihuza kandi zitari zanduye ahubwo zigaragaza itandukaniro rinini ry'imiterere.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateje ibibazo bikomeye mu buvuzi, siyansi, imibereho myiza n'imyifatire y'abantu mu Bushinwa no ku isi.
Ubushakashatsi ku nkomoko y'inyamaswa zanduye HCoVs butanga uburyo bwo gusobanukirwa amateka y'ibinyabuzima, imbaraga z'imikorere n'ibikumira ikwirakwira ry'ubwoko.
Ibi bishobora kuyobora cyangwa koroshya isuzuma ry'ikigega, uburyo bwo gucunga no kongera umubare w'amatungo (s) ya SARS-CoV-2, hamwe n'ingaruka zikomeye mu kurinda kugaruka mu gihe kizaza.
Muri iyi nyigisho, twerekanye mu buryo bw'inkoramutima inkomoko y'indwara zo mu matungo (zoonotic), ikwirakwira ryazo hagati y'amoko n'imiterere ya HCoVs.
By'umwihariko, turimo turushaho gusobanura neza inkomoko ya virusi ya HCoVs aho kuba ko ikomoka ku ngirabuzima fatizo zitera indwara mu mubiri nyuma yo kwinjira mu mubiri w'undi muntu.
Nanone kandi, twasuzumye imiterere y'ihindagurika rya HCoV aho ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bukunze kujyana no kugabanuka kw'ubwandu bw'agakoko gatera virusi.
Ingaruka z'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 zirasobanurwa hano.
CoV z'inyamaswa zari zizwi kuva mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1930.
Mbere yo gutandukanya bwa mbere ubwoko B814 bwa HCoV-229E mu mazuru y'umuntu wanduye ibicurane bisanzwe, CoVs zatandukanywaga mu nyamaswa zitandukanye zanduye nk'imbeba, imbeba, inka, ingurube, imbwa n'imbwa.
Mu myaka makumyabiri ishize, havumbuwe ubwoko bw'indwara ya HCoVs butandukanye.
Inkuru ngufi y'amateka y'ubwandu bwa HCoV mu mbonerahamwe ya mbere y'iyi mbonerahamwe (Imbonerahamwe ya 1) izatanga ibisobanuro byuzuye.
HCoV-229E yabanje gutandukanywa n'indwara y'ubuhumekero y'abarwayi bafite indwara y'ubuhumekero bwo hejuru mu 1966, nyuma yaho iza kwisanzura mu bwoko bw'ingirabuzimafatizo ya WI-38 yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
Abarwayi banduye HCoV-229E bagaragaweho ibimenyetso by'ibicurane bisanzwe, birimo umutwe, isesemi, kubabara, umuriro n'ububabare bw'izuru, umuriro n'inkorora bigaragara mu bice 10~20%.
Nyuma mu 1967, HCoV-OC43 yatandukanyijwe n'uburyo bwo gupima organ culture n'uburyo bwo kwanduzanya (serial passage) mu bwonko bw'abana b'imbeba.
Imiterere y'ubwandu bwa HCoV-OC43 isa n'iyo iterwa na HCoV-229E, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza itandukaniro hagati y'ubwandu bw'izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi nka grippe, virusi na rhinovirus.
HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43 byombi byandura ku isi hose, kandi bikunze gukwirakwira mu mpeshyi, mu bihe by'ubukonje cyangwa ubukonje.
Ubusanzwe, iyo mikorobe n'iyo mikorobe bitwara igihe kitageze ku cyumweru, bigakurikirwa n'ibyumweru bibiri by'indwara.
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abaganga, abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza banduye HCoV-229E barwaye ibicurane bisanzwe.
Abarwayi bake bafite ubwirinzi bw'umubiri budafite imbaraga bagaragaza ubwandu bukabije bw'indwara.
"SARS, izwi kandi nka ""virusi itera indwara z'ibihaha"", ni yo virusi ya mbere ya virusi itera HCoV mu mateka y'abantu kandi icyorezo cy'indwara ya SARS-CoV ni cyo HCoV ya gatatu yamenyekanye".
Icyorezo cya mbere cya SARS cyamenyekanye mu mpera za 2002 mu ntara ya Guangdong mu Bushinwa.
Icyorezo cya SARS cyateje abantu 8,096 bandura n'abantu 774 bahitanywe nacyo, cyakwirakwiriye mu bihugu byinshi no ku migabane myinshi.
Uretse abafite uburwayi bukomeye, byatekerejwe ko buri gisebe gishobora gutera ibibazo bibiri by'uburwayi, hamwe n'igihe cyo gutegura iminsi 4 kugeza ku minsi 7 aho udutsi tw'agakoko tugaragara ku munsi wa 10 w'uburwayi.
Abarwayi banduye SARS-CoV mu mizo ya mbere bagaragaza ibimenyetso by'ububabare bw'umubiri, umutwe, umuriro, malariya n'ubukonje bukabije, bikurikirwa no guhumeka nabi, inkorora n'ihungabana nk'ibimenyetso.
Imyitozo yo gupima imikorere y'umwijima, no kongera ingano ya creatine kinase ni ibintu bisanzwe mu bipimo bya SARS.
Kugabanya ibyago byo kwangirika kw'ibihaha (diffuse alveolar damage), kongera ingirabuzima fatizo mu mubiri (epithelial cell proliferation), no kongera ingirabuzima fatizo mu mubiri (macrophages) byagiye bigaragara mu barwayi ba SARS.
Nibura 20-30% by'abarwayi nyuma yaho baba bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane no guhumeka.
Uretse mu nzira y'ubuhumekero yo hasi, ingingo nyinshi z'umubiri, harimo n'inda, impyiko n'impyiko zishobora kwandura muri ibi bihe bikomeye by'indwara, akenshi ziterwa n'ingaruka za cytokine, zishobora guhitana cyane cyane abarwayi batagira ubudahangarwa.
Virusi yatangiriye gutandukanywa n'udufashi tw'ibicurane bya Ebola twavumbuwe na mwene wabo wa Ebola wari wavuye i Guangzhou ajya muri Hong Kong.
Kuva icyo gihe, hagiye hakorwa ubushakashatsi ku cyorezo cya HCoV.
HCoV-NL63 yatandukanyijwe n'umwana w'amezi 7 wo mu Buholandi mu mpera za 2004.
Iyo ndwara iboneka cyane cyane mu bana bato, mu bageze mu za bukuru no mu barwayi bafite uburwayi bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
Kurwara coryza, conjunctivitis, umuriro, n'uburwayi bwo mu maso ni ibintu bikunze kugaragara mu banduye HCoV-NL63.
Ubushakashatsi bwigenga bwagaragaje ko hari uburwayi bumwe bwigenga bwabonetse mu gishushanyo cy'izuru ry'umwana w'amezi 8 urwaye kanseri y'ibihaha mu Buholandi.
Nubwo yavumbuwe mu Buholandi, nta gushidikanya ko yakwirakwiriye ku isi hose.
Uduce duto tw'ingirabuzimafatizo twa HCoV-NL63 tugereranywaho kuba ari two twateje nibura 4.7% by'indwara zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, kandi zigaragara cyane mu itumba, mu itumba no mu itumba.
HCoV-NL63 ifitanye isano n'indwara ya Crohn's-Blial Syndrome, izwi kandi ku izina rya croup.
Mu mwaka ushize, virusi ya HCoV-HKU1 yagaragaye bwa mbere mu mugabo w'imyaka 71 wari wahise ajyanwa mu bitaro kubera indwara y'ibihaha n'ibihaha i Hong Kong.
Uretse indwara z'ibihaha n'iz'ibihaha z'abaturage, bivugwa ko HCoV-HKU1 ifitanye isano n'indwara y'ibihaha ikomeye.
Kimwe na HCoV-NL63, HCoV-229E na HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 yabonetse ku isi hose, ituma habaho ubwandu bworoheje.
Izo HCoV zose uko ari enye n'itsinda ryazo byagiye byigarurira abantu kandi akenshi ntibishobora guhinduka ngo bitere indwara nyinshi, nubwo impanuka zabaye kubera impamvu zitazwi nk'uko bimeze ku cyorezo cya HCoV-NL63, giherutse kuvugwa ko cyateje indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero mu Bushinwa.
Muri rusange, iyo izo HCoVs zishoboye gutandukana neza no kwihanganira abantu muri rusange, na zo ziba zidafite ubukana cyangwa ziteza akaga.
MERS-CoV yatangiriye gutandukanywa mu 2012 mu bihaha by'umurwayi w'imyaka 60 wari urwaye indwara ikomeye y'ibihaha n'impyiko muri Arabiya Sawudite.
Kubera ko abenshi mu bantu banduye bagaragaye ko bakomoka mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, hari amakuru avuga ko hari abandi bantu bakwirakwiriye mu bihugu bitandukanye by'i Burayi no muri Tuniziya.
Icyorezo cya kabiri cyabaye muri Koreya y'Epfo mu 2015 aho abantu 186 bemejwe ko banduye.
Ibimenyetso bya MERS bisa n'ibya SARS, igaragaza indwara y'ibihaha.
Icyakora, bitandukanye na SARS, abarwayi benshi ba MERS na bo barwaye indwara z'impyiko, ari na yo mpamvu nyamukuru ituma indwara ya MERS itandukana n'indwara ziterwa na HCoV.
Abarenga 30% by'abarwayi bagaragaza ibimenyetso byo mu maraso, nk'umusonga no gusubiranamo.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, abantu basaga 2500 banduye bamaze kwemezwa mu byumba by'ubushakashatsi, kandi umubare w'abapfa ni 34.4%, bituma MERS-CoV iba imwe mu ndwara zangiza cyane abantu.
Hagati mu kwezi kwa 12 mu 2019, hari abarwayi ba SARS-CoV-2 basanganywe indwara y'ubuhumekero cyangwa y'ibicurane, icyo gihe ikaba yari ifitanye isano n'iyo mu Bushinwa, mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko icyorezo cyateye imbere mu buryo buhuje n'amategeko, cyateje SARS-CoV-2 kandi ko cyabaye ikibazo gikomeye ku buzima rusange ku isi kandi cyiswe icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, as byemejwe ko hari abantu 90,053 banduye ku isi, hamwe n'umubare w'abapfa kubera ubwandu bwa 3.4%..
By'umwihariko, umubare w'abishwe n'iki cyorezo muri Hubei, mu Bushinwa ni 4,2 ku ijana, mu gihe hanze yaho ari 1,2 ku ijana.
SARS-CoV-2 ituma indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye nk'iza SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zitangwa nk'umuriro, inkorora na dyspnea.
Nanone kandi, hari abarwayi bamwe na bamwe barwaye indwara y'igifu.
Indwara y'ibihaha ni kimwe mu bimenyetso by'iyo ndwara kandi ishobora kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse igatuma umuntu arwara indwara ikomeye yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
Nubwo SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 isa cyane kuko ingirabuzimafatizo za nucleotide zigera kuri 82%, ikora mu mashami atandukanye y'igiti cy'imiterere.
Ugereranyije na SARS-CoV ifite umubare munini w'impinduka, umubare w'impinduka za SARS-CoV-2 ni muto cyane, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko abantu bakira neza.
Hari ikindi kimenyetso cy'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 cyavuzwe ko gishobora kuba cyaratumye ikwirakwira ku isi mu buryo bwihuse.
Kugereranya no gusimbuza SARS-CoV-2 izindi HCoV esheshatu bigaragaza ibintu byinshi bihuriyeho n'itandukaniro.
Icya mbere, igihe cyo kwandura n'uburyo HCoV ikwirakwira birasa.
Muri iki gihe, SARS-CoV-2 ikurikiza imiterere rusange y'izindi HCoV esheshatu.
Icya kabiri ni uko uburemere bw'ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bushingiye ku bwoko bwa SARS-CoV n'ubundi bwoko bw'izindi HCoVs enye: HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63).
Ku rundi ruhande, ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bugaragaza ibimenyetso bisanzwe bigaragara mu banduye HCoVs, byibasira abaturage, harimo no kutagira ibimenyetso bidasanzwe, byoroheje cyangwa nta bimenyetso.
Ku rundi ruhande, umubare muto w'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 ushobora kugaragara nk'uko bigaragara mu banduye SARS-CoV, ariko umubare muto cyane.
Icya gatatu, ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 na ryo rigaragaza ibimenyetso by'imiterere ishimishije ya HCoVs n'abaturage ku buryo buhabanye n'ubwa SARS-CoV.
Ku ruhande rumwe, SARS-CoV-2 yari ifite imiterere ihwanye n'iyo muri HCoVs zisanzwe zisanzwe.
Ku rundi ruhande, biracyari ngombwa kumenya niba ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bugabanuka nyuma yo kuvumburwa mu bantu nk'uko byagenze kuri SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV.
Mu gusoza, kimwe na za HCoVs zindi, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugaragara mu bimenyetso by'umwanda.
Ubushakashatsi buzakorwa mu gihe kiri imbere buzasuzuma niba SARS-CoV-2 yandura binyuze mu muhogo w'uruhu yagize uruhare rukomeye mu gukwirakwiza SARS-CoV.
Ni ibintu by'ingenzi cyane kureba niba SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugaragaza imiterere nk'iyo HCoVs zigaragaramo.
Icyakora, ibintu biranga SARS-CoV-2 birimo ubukana, ubwandu n'ubukana bw'ubwandu nyuma y'aho ahantu mu bantu bizagira ingaruka ku iherezo ry'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Amoko yose uko ari ane y'abantu basanze HCoVs ziterwa n'indwara ziterwa n'indwara z'ibyorezo ari zimwe n'iz'abantu.
Mu yandi magambo, birashoboka ko abantu bahindutse bakagira imiterere nk'iy'izo HCoVs enye.
Mu yandi magambo, byombi bishobora kuba byaturutse ku bantu ba kera ba HCoV.
HCoVs ziterwa n'indwara zikomeye mu bantu n'abantu banduye HCoV zikomeye zarakemutse.
Kugira ngo ibyo bibe, HCoVs zigomba kwiyongera mu bantu ku buryo buhagije kugira ngo zitume habaho ihinduka ry'imiterere ry'ubwoko bwazo, bityo ngo zishobore kurwanya impamvu z'ibihano by'ubwirinzi.
Muri ubwo buryo, igihe kirekire SARS-CoV-2 imaze mu cyorezo kandi abantu benshi bayanduye, ni cyo cyatuma bishoboka ko ishobora kwihanganira abantu.
Iyo ubwandu bwateye, gukwirakwira hagati y'abantu bishobora kuba ingorabahizi cyane binyuze mu kwirinda cyangwa izindi ngamba zo kwirinda indwara zitandura.
Mu gihe cy'imyaka myinshi, ibihugu bine byabonye ko CoV zigenda mu baturage, bigatuma haba ibicurane mu barobyi b'imbeba.
Iyo mikorobe ntiyagombye kuba mu mubiri w'umuntu cyangwa w'inyamaswa.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zandura ntizihuza neza n'abantu kandi ntizishobora gukwirakwira mu bantu.
Kugira ngo umuntu umwe cyangwa benshi bamugire, biba ngombwa ko bakomeza kubaho mu mubiri w'inyamaswa.
SARS-CoV-2 ifite ibimenyetso byinshi bisa n'ibya SARS-CoV/MERS-CoV n'izindi HCoVs zanduye.
Ibyo bishobora gukwirakwira cyane nk'uko ubwandu bwa HCOV bushobora gukwirakwira mu baturage, nibura mu gihe turimo.
Icyakora, irandura cyane kurusha izindi HCoVs zisanzwe kandi ntizigira ubwandu bwinshi nk'ubw'indwara ya SARS-CoV cyangwa MERS-CoV.
Kugeza ubu, ntibiramenyekana niba ishobora kuba ikora neza mu bantu kandi ikagenda mu bantu nta hantu na hamwe ikinga cyangwa ngo igire aho ikinga mu mubiri w'inyamaswa.
Mbere yo kuganira ku nkomoko y'inyamaswa za HCoVs, byaba byiza tuganiriye ku bisobanuro n'imiterere y'ihindagurika, ibinyabuzima, ibigega, uburyo bwo gutandukanya no guteza imbere HCoVs.
Inyamaswa ishobora kuba ihumeka HCoV mu buryo bw'ihindagurika iyo ifite inkomoko ya kera cyane ihuriyeho cyane mu buryo bw'imiterere ya nucleotide.
Akenshi virusi iba ifite ubumara kandi ntibangamiye aho iba.
Ikindi kandi, ikigega cy'imikorere ya HCoV gikomeza kandi kirambye.
Mu bihe byose, abanduye banduye mu buryo bw'ibanze kandi ni bo bafite ubwoko bwa HCoV cyangwa virusi y'inkoko.
Ku rundi ruhande, iyo HCoV nshya igeze ku muyoboro mushya mbere cyangwa hafi yo kuwuzana ku bantu, ntiyihuza n'uwo muyoboro mushya kandi akenshi iba ifite ubwandu.
Iyo mikorobe iba imaze gushinga ingoyi, ishobora kuba ari yo soko y'indwara kandi ikaba ifite uruhare rukomeye mu gutuma ikwirakwira ahantu ishobora kurasa umuntu.
HCoV ishobora kugerageza indwara y'icyorezo mu gihe itakomeje kwanduza mu buryo bworoshye.
Gusa uretse ko nta kindi kintu cyihariye, HCoVs zishobora kubaho mu mubiri utandukanye kandi zishobora gutera ingaruka zikomeye cyane zitwara igihe kirekire mbere yo kugaragara.
Aha nanone, umuntu ufite uburwayi bwo mu mubiri wa nyuma aba ari we ufite uburwayi bw'ibanze.
Ibitabo by'ubushakashatsi ku ndwara z'amatungo byerekana ko ubushakashatsi bwa buri munsi bugaragaza ko abantu bo muri SARS bafite amateka y'imikoranire n'inyamaswa z'imikino.
Ubushakashatsi bwa seriveri bukurikira bugaragaza ko abacuruzi b'amatungo bafite umubare munini wa SARS-CoV IgG ugereranyije n'abandi baturage.
Ibisimba by'inyamaswa (Paguma larvata) n'imbeba zo mu bwoko bwa racoon mu bucuruzi bw'amatungo ni byo bya mbere byagaragaye ko bitwara virusi zisa n'izisa n'iza SARS-CoV.
