Mu kwezi k'Ukuboza 2019, coronavirus yo mu mwaka wa 2019 (2019-nCoV) yateje icyorezo, ubu cyiswe coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) kandi cyiswe SARS-CoV-2 (indwara y'ibyorezo y'indwara y'ibyorezo).
