Menya ko nubwo COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, ubumenyi n'ubunararibonye dufite bigenda byiyongera buhoro buhoro bitewe n'ubushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubumenyi bw'ubuvuzi; bityo rero, uburyo bwo gusuzuma no kuvura burakomeza kuvugururwa.
Urugero, raporo y'ibanze y'ubushakashatsi n'amabwiriza y'ubuvuzi kuri COVID-19 yatanzwe n'Ikigo cy'Ubuzima cya Repubulika y'Abashinwa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), hagati ya 16 Mutarama 2020 na 3 Werurwe 2020, yatangaje impinduka zirindwi z'ubwoko hamwe n'ibindi bintu bihinduka cyane.
