Ibimenyetso by'indwara: (1) umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso by'indwara y'ubuhumekero; (2) ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) ingirabuzima fatizo zera zigaragaza neza, kugabanuka, cyangwa kugabanuka kw'umubare w'utugingo ngengabuzima mu cyiciro cya mbere.
Gusuzuma urubanza rwemejwe bigomba gushingira ku birego bikekwa hamwe n'ikintu kimwe cy'indwara cyangwa igihamya cya seroloji gikurikira: (1) ibizamini bya PCR byerekana neza SARS-CoV-2; (2) ifoto cyangwa videwo ikwirakwizwa vuba ya sisitemu yose igaragaza imiterere ikomeye ya coronavirusi zizwi; (3) igaragaza neza IgM antibody na IgG antibody kuri SARS-CoV-2 mu isuzuma rya serum; cyangwa impinduka ya SARG-CoV-2-IgG igaragaza IgG kuva kuri negative ikajya kuri positive, cyangwa se igipimo cy'indwara kizamuka inshuro ≥4 mu gihe cyo gukira cy'umuntu uri mu bihe bikomeye.
