Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidasanzwe kandi abantu banduye bashobora kutagira ibimenyetso.
Ibimenyetso by'uburwayi bikunze kugaragara ni umuriro (88%) n'umuhogo usanzwe (68%).
Ibimenyetso by'uburwayi ni umunaniro, guhumeka, kugira iseseme, guhumeka nabi, ububabare mu ngingo no mu mubiri, kuribwa mu muhogo, umutwe, kubabara, gusubiranamo, gucibwamwo, cyangwa cyanoze. OMS yatangaje ko umuntu umwe muri batandatu arwaye kandi ko guhumeka bimugora.
Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no kurwanya indwara (CDC) gitanga ibimenyetso byihutirwa nko guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu gatuza cyangwa mu mwete, guhungabana mu buryo butunguranye, kubyuka bidakomeye, no kugira isura nziza cyangwa iminwa; inama yihutirwa y'ubuvuzi iragirwa iyo ibyo bimenyetso bihari.Igikorwa cy'uburwayi gishobora gutera indwara ikomeye y'ibihaha, indwara y'ubuhumekero idakira cyane, isesemi, sepsis, sepsis, guhindagurika kwa septic no gupfa.
Bamwe mu banduye bashobora kuba nta bimenyetso bagaragaza, nta bimenyetso byo kwa muganga ariko bafite ibipimo byemeza ko banduye, bityo abashakashatsi bagaragaje ko abantu bari babanye n'abantu banduye bagomba gukurikiranwa cyane no gusuzumwa kugira ngo birinde kwandura.
