Nubwo hari ingaruka zo kwitarura abantu mu modoka zitwara abagenzi mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu byinshi byateguye gucyura abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba ambasade, mbere na mbere binyuze mu guhagarika gari ya moshi, abayobozi b'Ubushinwa bakaba baremeye ko bava muri uwo mujyi.
Canada, Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Australia, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage na Thailand ni bimwe mu bihugu bya mbere byatangiye gucyura abaturage babyo.
Pakistan yavuze ko itazongera kwirukana abaturage bayo bari mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare, Burezili yirukanye abaturage 34 b'Abanyabrezili cyangwa bene wabo, hamwe n'Abanyafurika bane, Umushina n'Umuhindi.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'u Buhinde bahagurutse mu ndege yabo iherereye muri Polonye mu gihe indege yabo yari ivuye muri Brezili yari igeze aho ihagarara.
Abanyamerika bavuye muri Brazil bajya i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato mu kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brasilia.
Mu munsi umwe, Abanyakanada 215 (176 bari mu ndege ya mbere, na 39 bari mu ndege ya kabiri yari itwaye na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika) bavuye i Wuhan bajya muri Trenton CFB kugira ngo bashyirwe mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abaturage 185 ba Canada ivuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan yageze ku kibuga cy'indege cya CFB Trenton.
Abakozi ba Australia bakuye abaturage 277 hagati ya tariki ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare ku kirwa cya Christmas Island cyagombaga kubakwa mu buryo bwihariye kugira ngo abantu bajye mu kato.
Indi ndege yavaga muri Nouvelle-Zélande yageze muri Auckland ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare; abagenzi bayo (harimo n'abaturutse muri Ositaraliya no mu nyanja ya Pasifika) bari bashyizwe mu kato ku cyambu cya Whangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku ya 15 Gashyantare, guverinoma ya Amerika yatangaje ko igiye gutabara abaturage bayo ikoresheje ubwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abagenzi 129 b'Abanyakanada bari birukanywe mu ndege ya Diamond Princess yageze i Trenton, Ontario.
