"Gukaraba intoki n'isabuni kenshi ""mu gihe cy'ingenzi"" ku manywa, bigabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'indwara y'ibinyigishi na kolera zandurira mu kanwa".
