Gutanga inama ku bihereranye no gukaraba intoki n'isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myanzuro ifatwa, bigatuma abantu barushaho kumenya akamaro ko gukaraba intoki kandi bishobora guhindura imyifatire y'abantu.
