Nk'uko byemezwa n'ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima (OSHA), ibyago byo guhura n'abantu benshi n'abandi bakozi ni bike cyane, kandi hari ingamba z'ubwirinzi zisabwa, zirimo gukaraba intoki, gukangurira abakozi kuguma mu rugo iyo barwaye, guhumeka neza, guhanagura imyanda buri munsi, no guhanagura no guhanagura udukoko mu kazi.
Abakozi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura harimo abakenera kwihererana cyangwa guhura n'abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba barwaye COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura bitewe n'ubwandu bukomeje mu baturage cyangwa ingendo zo hanze y'igihugu.
Ibyo bikubiyemo abakozi bakorana n'abandi, urugero nk'abanyeshuri, abantu benshi n'abajya guhaha.
