BAngiotensin conversion enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni enzyme ifatanye n'urusobe rw'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu mara.
ACE2 igenzura ibikorwa bya enzyme ihuza ibinyabiziga (ACE) igabanya ingano ya angiotensin-II no kongera Ang (1-7) bigatuma iba intego ikomeye yo kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 ikora kandi nk'umuyoboro winjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za coronaviruses zimwe na zimwe.
Ubwoko bw'ingirabuzimafatizo y'umuntu yitwa hACE2.
Ingingo ya Angiotensin 2 ni ingirabuzimafatizo ya zinc irimo ironloenzyme iri ku gice cy'imbere mu mubiri n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 igizwe n'agace ka N-terminal peptidase M2 hamwe n'agace ka C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transport domain.
ACE2 ni ubwoko bwa poroteyine y'uruhu, ifite igice cy'umubiri gikora neza mu buryo bwa enzymatic, kigaragaza ibice by'imbere by'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bihaha no mu zindi ngingo.
Agace k'inyuma y'ingirabuzimafatizo ka ACE2 gaterwa n'urugero rw'agakoko gatera indwara binyuze mu mushongi witwa hematopoietic, maze poroteyine itera indwara ikirukanwa mu maraso, amaherezo ikagera mu musarani.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifata mu mubiri ibice byinshi by'ibice by'ubuhumekero by'ubwoko bwa II, uturemangingo tw'intanga duto, uturemangingo tw'imitsi n'utw'imitsi y'umutima n'utw'ingingo z'umubiri mu bice byinshi by'umubiri.
ACE2 MRNA iboneka mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'imbere mu mubiri no mu gice cy'imbere mu mubiri.
Inshingano y'ibanze ya ACE2 ni uguhagarara nk'igicumbi cy'ingufu za ACE.
ACE igabanya igipimo cya angiotensin I mu giterwa n'umuvuduko w'amaraso (angiotensin II).
ACE2 nayo ifata amino acide phenylalanine yo mu gice cy'umushongi wa karuboni (carboxyl-terminal amino acid phenylalanine) ikayivanga na angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) ikayivanga na angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg -Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
